      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STEELY DAWN (3) lines up chasing another win after getting around the 411m at this track in a slick 23.30 two back then following up with a 23.32 win at this track over 411m last time. Flying lately and expected to go close again. MIDNIGHT BULLET (1) had been racing well with a Grade 5 win three back then placed next time before missing the frame latest at this track. Has good speed and aided by the cherry draw. Can find the frame this time. SHE LIES EASY (2) is first up since finishing fourth (23.82) in a Grade 5 at this track over 411m six months ago. Looks well placed here and has the ability. Go well. KICKER SPLASH (8) is always a threat when she races at this journey.",
